---
import Base from '../../hubs/dev0/layouts/Base.astro';
import ToolLayout from '../../hubs/dev0/components/ToolLayout.astro';
---
<Base
  title="UUID & ULID Generator + Timestamp Decoder, 100% local | dev0.dev"
  description="Generate UUID v4/v7 in bulk and decode the embedded timestamp from UUIDv7 and ULID. Runs entirely in your browser."
>
  <ToolLayout name="UUID & ULID Toolbox">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <!-- Generate panel -->
      <div class="rounded-sm border border-rule bg-raised overflow-hidden">
        <div class="px-4 py-2.5 border-b border-rule flex items-center justify-between">
          <span class="label">Generate</span>
        </div>
        <div class="px-4 py-3 border-b border-rule flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
          <select
            id="uuid-kind"
            class="text-sm font-mono px-2 py-1 rounded-sm bg-bg border border-rule text-ink focus:outline-none focus:border-accent"
          >
            <option value="v4">UUID v4 (random)</option>
            <option value="v7">UUID v7 (time-ordered)</option>
          </select>
          <input
            id="uuid-count"
            type="number"
            min="1"
            max="1000"
            value="5"
            class="w-20 text-sm font-mono px-2 py-1 rounded-sm bg-bg border border-rule text-ink focus:outline-none focus:border-accent"
          />
          <button id="uuid-gen" class="text-[11px] font-medium px-2.5 py-1 rounded-sm bg-bg border border-accent text-accent transition-colors">Generate</button>
          <button id="uuid-copyall" class="text-[11px] font-medium px-2.5 py-1 rounded-sm bg-bg border border-rule text-muted transition-colors ml-auto">copy all</button>
        </div>
        <div id="uuid-list" class="min-h-[140px] max-h-[360px] overflow-y-auto"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Decode panel -->
      <div class="rounded-sm border border-rule bg-raised overflow-hidden">
        <div class="px-4 py-2.5 border-b border-rule flex items-center justify-between">
          <span class="label">Decode</span>
          <span id="uuid-kind-badge" class="text-[10px] font-mono px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-sm bg-bg text-muted">—</span>
        </div>
        <input
          id="uuid-decode-input"
          type="text"
          class="w-full p-4 bg-transparent text-sm font-mono text-ink focus:outline-none placeholder:text-muted border-b border-rule"
          placeholder="018fe5b2-0400-7000-8000-000000000000 or a ULID"
        />
        <div id="uuid-decode-time" class="px-4 py-4 min-h-[100px]">
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">paste an id to inspect it…</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p slot="explainer">
      UUID v4 is fully random; UUID v7 and ULID prefix a 48-bit Unix-millisecond
      timestamp, so they sort by creation time and you can read that instant straight
      back out of the id. Paste one into the decoder to see it. UUID v4 carries no
      time, so there is nothing to decode. Generation and decoding both run entirely
      in this tab; no id is ever uploaded.
    </p>
  </ToolLayout>
</Base>
<script>
  import { uuidSection } from '../../hubs/dev0/scripts/tools/uuid';
  uuidSection();
</script>
